data.description: This small town beauty is perfectly situated in the outermost North-East residential neighborhood in Frederick. Location provides close enough proximity to access anything you might need in less than five minutes while providing peace and quiet upon your return home.  The front door faces South and covered back patio faces North allowing you to enjoy morning coffee or evening tea outside without the glare of a rising or setting sun. Inside it is a partial open floor concept with large living area open to a formal dining space convenient for entertaining friends or family. It has 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The Master Suite includes one of those as a private bath and features a spacious walk-in closet. The home has an attached double car garage with ample storage space while vehicles are parked inside and safe from the elements. Last but certainly not least you will be pleased to find a neighborhood park only one block away. The park provides a place for kiddos to run and play without the worry of busy traffic as there are no thru streets! No kiddos…no worries the park is great for a morning run or a walk for the family dog or a simple sit under a shade tree.
